<h3>Re: [SOLVED] Annoying Random Logout</h3>
<div class="postmsg">
<p>I had a random log out issue on one of my installs, seemed very weird, no error though.&#160; I noticed it happened after installing Teamviewer, I removed it and seemed fine, but after installing Libre office I would get Logged off every time I attempted to download anything.&#160; I did run all updates and did distro upgrade but to no avail.&#160; I ended up reinstalling Parrot.&#160; We really enjoy this OS at work, great for testing environments&#160; and for home use.&#160; I believe it could have been more of a hardware issue, I have this on another Dell Laptop at work and works great.</p>
<p class="postedit"><em>Last edited by Alazo (2017-02-26 21:37:01)</em></p>
