<h3>Re: [SOLVED] Annoying Random Logout</h3>
<div class="postmsg">
<p>Teamviewer is not going to give you a problem like this.. If it is installed right.&#160; I use Teamviewer daily to help people i never have any problems,<br/>I am guessing you may have it installed incorrectly.&#160; also a note that you must have wine32 installed as well and also architecture</p>
