<h3>Re: [SOLVED] Annoying Random Logout</h3>
<div class="postmsg">
<p>My Personal Experience with the exact same issue. I use parrot LITE coz i want to choose what gets installed. And when ever i perform a distro update (which would upgrade several packages and install new too) I always ended up with the exact same problem. Everything working well until you open application like VLC,Blender, Kdenlive. etc. i always ended up being logged out (along with a 2 sec black screen). So i reinstalled the distro, now i don&#039;t dist-upgrade, I only upgrade specific things that i need., So far so good. <br/>Has anyone found a fix for this?</p>
</div>
